<item>
            <title>[LU-4574] Failed to mount second OST</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4574</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Created two OSTs in active/active configuration. When mounting both on one node getting error.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;root@n3 ~&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;# mount -t lustre /dev/mapper/OSS_DATA_02 /lustre/data02&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;root@n3 ~&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;# mount -t lustre /dev/mapper/OSS_DATA_01 /lustre/data01&lt;br/&gt;
mount.lustre: mount /dev/mapper/OSS_DATA_01 at /lustre/data01 failed: Operation already in progress&lt;br/&gt;
The target service is already running. (/dev/mapper/OSS_DATA_01)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At the same time i can mount /dev/mapper/OSS_DATA_01 on second OSS node(n4)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>RHEL6.4 2.6.32-358.23.2.el6_lustre.x86_64. HA MDT/MGS + 2 OSS nodes(n3,n4).&lt;br/&gt;
2 OST filesystems.</environment>
